name: Ai Tribes
description:
Memory part 2

I have a dream last night about "Asianizing" and "Westernizing". I believe this is the message from my ancestors. It resonates with McLuhan's thesis about culture and I quote "innovative tools makes the existing culture obsolete. Is it really true? This painting is guided by mushroom artifacts and neural networks. Artist; Steve Manzano (@memoryprojects)
